::Prowl::

Prowl's eyes widen slightly at Iron Raptor's kiss. Yet another wave of 
excitement sweeps over him and his hands tighten around her.

The shift of the weight causes the two bots to lose their balance, falling 
over into the soft undergrowth, Prowl still holding Iron Raptor tightly and 
kissing her.
